Goldman Sachs Exploring ‘Possible Sale’ of Litton Loan Servicing Business

-- B y   C h r i s t i n e   H a r p e r
-- 
2011-03-15T22:08:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-15/goldman-sachs-group-may-sell-litton-home-mortgage-servicing-operations.html
  Goldman Sachs Group Inc. (GS)  may sell
its Litton Loan Servicing unit, the New York-based company said
today.  “Goldman Sachs is exploring strategic options for Litton
Loan Servicing, which include a possible sale,” said  Michael
DuVally , a spokesman for the firm in  New York . The potential
sale was reported earlier today by the New York Times.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Christine Harper in New York at 
